<subSubSection pageId="0" pageNumber="362" type="diagnosis">
<paragraph blockId="0.[1236,2117,753,1384]" pageId="0" pageNumber="362">• Small to medium-sized marsupials, with long pointed snouts, rather small mouse-like ears, short tails and short limbs.</paragraph>
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6621744" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6621744" box="[1238,1426,874,903]" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6621744/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="0" pageNumber="362" startId="0.[1238,1251,874,903]" targetBox="[1275,2114,928,1091]" targetPageId="0">
